items.Name: Rengoku
items.Description:
Rengoku - 3D Wooden Panel inspired by popular Anime 'Demon slayer'.
Crafted from high-quality natural wood, this panel is made with a keen attention
to detail and a passion for the Anime lover world. On our site each and every panel is expertly carved to create
a stunning 3D effect, bringing the Anime characters to life in a whole new way.
